title: #92Noon! Anderson/Florio/Russo/LaVelle
description: Gophers Baseball coach John Anderson joined PA to recap winning the Big 10 Tournament and look ahead to the #Gophers hosting a regional this weekend, ProFootballTalk's Mike Florio talks NFL, Michael Russo of The Athletic joins PA to talk about the Stanley Cup Final and the Star Tribune's LaVelle E. Neal III talks all things baseball!
